<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Clã das Barras - Treino Semanal</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial Black', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #0a0a0a;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        /* MARCA D'ÁGUA - LOGO CLÃ DAS BARRAS */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle, transparent 30%, rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.03) 31%, rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.03) 45%, transparent 46%),
                radial-gradient(circle, transparent 65%, rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.03) 66%, rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.03) 70%, transparent 71%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: -1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        body::after {
            content: "CLÃ DAS BARRAS";
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-45deg);
            font-size: 80px;
            color: rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.03);
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            z-index: -1;
            pointer-events: none;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        
        .watermark-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .watermark-logo {
            position: absolute;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            opacity: 0.04;
        }
        
        .watermark-logo:nth-child(1) { top: 10%; left: 5%; transform: rotate(-15deg); }
        .watermark-logo:nth-child(2) { top: 60%; right: 5%; transform: rotate(15deg); }
        .watermark-logo:nth-child(3) { bottom: 10%; left: 30%; transform: rotate(-10deg); }
        
        .wm-circle {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: 8px solid #e60012;
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .wm-circle::before {
            content: "CLÃ DAS BARRAS";
            position: absolute;
            width: 85%;
            height: 85%;
            border: 3px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .wm-athlete {
            width: 40%;
            height: 60%;
            background: #e60012;
            clip-path: polygon(20% 0%, 80% 0%, 100% 20%, 100% 80%, 80% 100%, 20% 100%, 0% 80%, 0% 20%);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.95);
            border: 3px solid #e60012;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #e60012;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .logo-circle {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border: 4px solid #e60012;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #000;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.3);
        }
        
        .logo-circle::before {
            content: "CLÃ DAS BARRAS";
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #fff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .athlete-icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 70px;
            background: #e60012;
            clip-path: polygon(25% 0%, 75% 0%, 100% 25%, 100% 75%, 75% 100%, 25% 100%, 0% 75%, 0% 25%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #e60012;
            font-size: 32px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.3);
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .info-section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.9);
            border: 2px solid #e60012;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .info-box label {
            display: block;
            color: #e60012;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .info-box input {
            width: 100%;
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #444;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 5px 0;
            outline: none;
        }
        
        .week-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .day-card {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.9);
            border: 2px solid #333;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            min-height: 200px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .day-card.active {
            border-color: #e60012;
            background: rgba(31, 5, 5, 0.9);
        }
        
        .day-header {
            background: #e60012;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 8px;
            margin: -15px -15px 10px -15px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .day-card.rest .day-header {
            background: #444;
        }
        
        .exercise-list {
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .exercise-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            font-size: 12px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        
        .exercise-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .sets-reps {
            color: #e60012;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .notes-section {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.9);
            border: 2px solid #e60012;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .notes-section h3 {
            color: #e60012;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .notes-section textarea {
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.9);
            border: 1px solid #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            min-height: 100px;
            resize: vertical;
            font-family: inherit;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e60012;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e60012;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        @media print {
            body { background: #fff; }
            .container { border: 3px solid #000; background: #fff; }
            body::before, body::after, .watermark-container { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- MARCAS D'ÁGUA REPETIDAS NO FUNDO -->
    <div class="watermark-container">
        <div class="watermark-logo">
            <div class="wm-circle">
                <div class="wm-athlete"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="watermark-logo">
            <div class="wm-circle">
                <div class="wm-athlete"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="watermark-logo">
            <div class="wm-circle">
                <div class="wm-athlete"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-circle">
                <div class="athlete-icon"></div>
            </div>
            <h1>Plano de Treino Semanal</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">CLÃ DAS BARRAS - GT DE TREINAMENTO</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-section">
            <div class="info-box">
                <label>Atleta</label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Nome completo">
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
                <label>Nível</label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Iniciante/Intermediário/Avançado">
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
                <label>Semana</label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Data: ___/___/______">
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="week-grid">
            <div class="day-card active">
                <div class="day-header">Segunda</div>
                <ul class="exercise-list">
                    <li>Pull-ups <span class="sets-reps">4x8</span></li>
                    <li>Push-ups <span class="sets-reps">4x15</span></li>
                    <li>Agachamento <span class="sets-reps">3x20</span></li>
                    <li>Prancha <span class="sets-reps">3x45s</span></li>
                    <li>Dips <span class="sets-reps">3x10</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card active">
                <div class="day-header">Terça</div>
                <ul class="exercise-list">
                    <li>Barra fixa <span class="sets-reps">4x6</span></li>
                    <li>Flexão diamante <span class="sets-reps">3x12</span></li>
                    <li>Leg raises <span class="sets-reps">3x15</span></li>
                    <li>Superman <span class="sets-reps">3x20</span></li>
                    <li>Burpees <span class="sets-reps">3x10</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card rest">
                <div class="day-header">Quarta</div>
                <ul class="exercise-list">
                    <li style="text-align: center; color: #666; padding-top: 50px;">DESCANSO ATIVO</li>
                    <li style="text-align: center; color: #888; font-size: 11px;">Alongamento leve</li>
                    <li style="text-align: center; color: #888; font-size: 11px;">Caminhada 30min</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card active">
                <div class="day-header">Quinta</div>
                <ul class="exercise-list">
                    <li>Muscle-up neg <span class="sets-reps">4x5</span></li>
                    <li>Flexão archer <span class="sets-reps">3x8</span></li>
                    <li>Pistol squat <span class="sets-reps">3x6</span></li>
                    <li>L-sit <span class="sets-reps">3x20s</span></li>
                    <li>Pull-over <span class="sets-reps">3x8</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card active">
                <div class="day-header">Sexta</div>
                <ul class="exercise-list">
                    <li>Front lever tuck <span class="sets-reps">4x15s</span></li>
                    <li>Handstand wall <span class="sets-reps">3x30s</span></li>
                    <li>Dragon flag <span class="sets-reps">3x5</span></li>
                    <li>Row invertido <span class="sets-reps">4x10</span></li>
                    <li>Jump squat <span class="sets-reps">3x15</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card active">
                <div class="day-header">Sábado</div>
                <ul class="exercise-list">
                    <li>EMOM 20min <span class="sets-reps">Circuito</span></li>
                    <li>5 Pull-ups</li>
                    <li>10 Push-ups</li>
                    <li>15 Agachamentos</li>
                    <li style="color: #e60012; font-weight: bold;">Máximo rodadas!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card rest">
                <div class="day-header">Domingo</div>
                <ul class="exercise-list">
                    <li style="text-align: center; color: #666; padding-top: 50px;">DESCANSO TOTAL</li>
                    <li style="text-align: center; color: #888; font-size: 11px;">Recuperação muscular</li>
                    <li style="text-align: center; color: #888; font-size: 11px;">Mobilidade</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="notes-section">
            <h3>📝 Observações da Semana</h3>
            <textarea placeholder="Registre seu progresso, dificuldades e conquistas..."></textarea>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="badge">Personal Mark - Since 2024</div>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">CLÃ DAS BARRAS - Forja de Guerreiros</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
